SubjectBy-elections (3) - Peterborough - Sudbury - Ottawa West - Nepean
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of Peterborough - Sudbury - Ottawa West - Nepean, with polling to take place on October 19, 2015.
